{"tid":1770471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(倒數五日) 逃犯條例大力支持者！第五十四屆工展會！","createTime":"2019-12-05T09:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T13:05:30.000Z","uid":50810,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1d83b6afd9702ba3eedf73e9300b55374c1bd15a","tid":1770471,"uid":50810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第五十四屆工展會12月10-31日維園舉行<br />\n<br />\n主辦機構: 中華廠商聯合會（逃犯條例嘅大力支持者）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NUm9tb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NUm9tb.jpg&h=345088a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地點: 銅鑼灣維多利亞公園<br />\n日期: 2019年12月10日至30日 , 2019年12月31日(展會最後一天)<br />\n時間:上午11時至晚上8時</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkbpe.com.hk/web/subpage.php?mid=216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbpe.com.hk%2Fweb%2Fsubpage.php%3Fmid%3D216&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=7864e15f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkbpe.com.hk/web/subpage.php?mid=216</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goz6A7o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgoz6A7o.png&h=d4f10d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUNDsd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUNDsd4.png&h=c626fd79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af2Dsd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf2Dsd5.png&h=15dcde1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">為慶賀中華廠商會85周年誌慶<br />\n<br />\n故我們必須要大大力支持返佢個活動 <br />\n<br />\n大家記住一起入去shopping <br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣及天后入口仲有大型拱門設置 （文宣組唔好亂咁貼呀）<br />\n<br />\n10/12/2019 - 31/10/2019<br />\n<br />\n此外，今年工展會隨時有新嘢試食，「Tear Gas 放題」<br />\n<br />\n同場加映，驚謊為保護工展會水砲車將藍水對準展會發射<br />\n<br />\n展會內大量藍絲廢佬，藍店，一起shopping可融洽一下<br />\n<br />\n藍絲變黃絲，食粒TG即可<br />\n<br />\n此外<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林奠</span></strong></span>往年仲會出席開幕日，唔知今年會唔會一齊振興經濟呢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N44BYma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN44BYma.jpg&h=753b5711&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCja2NR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCja2NR.jpg&h=cb44c95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可 <br />\n香港警察，xx xx (太多，自己推post選填）</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c87c0a071a9309c8de7efeb0effa61e333327a01","tid":1770471,"uid":50810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:38:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cd9cbb9794b57dbd95a60c491fda557ae9cbaf3","tid":1770471,"uid":50810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad637ef144bdcf18daa479d9d1a9723000b73db7","tid":1770471,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNWdf8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNWdf8E.jpg&h=8384cbd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba7e1bc6d87d09da256e1b17903ba5d3e53e148f","tid":1770471,"uid":50810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfca0a7224a314a07c1d6548cfb0ed8fb5bfc3a4","tid":1770471,"uid":50810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"1f154a3cd3ea082dd2b3f21d4f6e863af1a07610","tid":1770471,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:39:34.000Z","msg":"有咩可以做"},{"pid":"4c3c869e4daeb25d7f5960cb0de7ccf93f9ceff3","tid":1770471,"uid":50810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:39:35.000Z","msg